{"tid":1365475,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[做個好市民] 如何對付懷疑請黑工嘅藍絲餐廳","createTime":"2019-07-25T15:54:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-25T16:17:37.000Z","uid":260482,"like":19,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"393ba45e8775354f71bc33caeb8cbcae1b54c325","tid":1365475,"uid":260482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T15:54:49.000Z","msg":"[ 幫係入境處做嘅朋友出post ]<br />\n<br />\n對於支持暴力嘅藍絲餐廳（e.g. 潮x），就算我地罷食，都一定仲有好多政治冷感嘅人照樣去幫襯。 <br />\n<br />\n其實如果發現果間餐廳有員工操普通話或唔純正廣東話，可以向我地入境處網上匿名舉報懷疑聘請黑工嘅餐廳， 部門收到舉報一定會做嘢，其實宜家好多小本經營嘅餐廳都有請黑工問題，拉都拉唔哂，所以有黑工嘅機會好大。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.gov.hk/tc/residents/immigration/investigation/onlinereportoffence.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gov.hk%2Ftc%2Fresidents%2Fimmigration%2Finvestigation%2Fonlinereportoffence.htm&d=VlhNwxbPYDbrmmiZclZ9hARUsGYs0X8VP9vM6mjQjJM%3D&h=d22989dd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.gov.hk/tc/residents/immigration/investigation/onlinereportoffence.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n電話：<br />\n入境事務處24小時舉報熱線：(852) 2824 1551<br />\n(舉報後獲提供一個檔案編號)<br />\n<br />\n傳真：<br />\n(852) 2824 1166<br />\n<br />\n電郵：<br />\nanti_crime@immd.gov.hk<br />\n<br />\n郵寄地址：<br />\n香港<br />\n九龍九龍灣<br />\n宏光道三十九號<br />\n宏天廣場五樓<br />\n入境事務處<br />\n<br />\n入得紀律部隊，就係想正當執法，打擊罪案，保障市民權益，而唔係助長歪風。希望大家幫手舉報問題食肆。<br />\n<br />\n同時，如果懷疑間餐廳有衞生問題，懷疑食物處理唔妥當，又可以向食環舉報。<br />\n<br />\n要反擊，唔一定要圍， 不如用番制度去對付問題。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rBCdkQ7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrBCdkQ7.jpg&h=e7b897bc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c66ee8e98c0e640eabab290d7386bb87a52204ac","tid":1365475,"uid":260482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T16:06:53.000Z","msg":"（持續更新）全面抵制奶共、送中餐廳店鋪<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1224502\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1224502</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n搵到有巴打之前出過依個post，歡迎各位持續更新，一齊做個好市民！"},{"pid":"67c0ae06c2bb82fec59c75739a681c9ce1720c08","tid":1365475,"uid":266879,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T16:07:07.000Z","msg":"留意   鐵路手制用法<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HYSpsB2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHYSpsB2.png&h=4be9f38d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d7af5b238d310f53372db1859518282f97011758","tid":1365475,"uid":275887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T16:09:07.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4a323899c415e850ba3c263ae27d131a807ed9a0","tid":1365475,"uid":256893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T16:17:37.000Z","msg":"仲有好多黑底洗黑錢酒樓 有請黑工"}]}